7/Neriame-Ringo-to-Kimi-300x300.jpg)\n\n| Original Title: | りんごと君 |\n| --- |\n| Artist: | ### [Neriame](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ \"Neriame Lyric Directory - Lyrical Nonsense\") 音莉飴 |\n| Tie-in: | [Spice and Wolf: Merchant Meets the Wise Wolf](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/ookami-to-koushinryou-merchant-meets-the-wise-wolf-theme-songs/ \"Spice and Wolf: Merchant Meets the Wise Wolf Lyrics\") Ookami to Koushinryou: Merchant Meets the Wise Wolf 狼と香辛料 MERCHANT MEETS THE WISE WOLF |\n| Release: | 2024.07.09 |\n| Lyricist: | Neriame |\n| Composer: | Akari (Neriame)・butter.D (MARUMOCHI) |\n| Arranger: | MARUMOCHI |\n| Video: | [View Video](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#video) |\n| Original Lyrics: | [Ringo to Kimi Lyrics (Romanized)](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/ \"Ringo to Kimi Lyrics (Romanized)\") |\n\n*   [LN](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#English \"English Translation\")\n*   [Original](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#Original \"Original Lyrics\")\n*   [SIDE-BY-SIDE](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#Side \"Side-by-side Comparison\")\n\nPlay \"Ringo to Kimi\" \n\n on Apple Music\n\n[Aa](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)[Aa](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)[Aa](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)\n\n[Left](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)[Center](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)\n\n[Dark](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)[Light](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)\n\n1.Sarasarariru Sararura\n\n2.Sarasararura Sarariru 3.\n\n4.Hello!\n\n5.Is someone waiting for you at home?\n\n6.Getting hungry, perking up my ears and nose,\n\n7.Yes, I can smell the delicious aroma.8.\n\n9.Chasing your shadow,\n\n10.I can’t reach you, once again,\n\n11.Today’s mood is altogether,\n\n12.Exceptionally great!!13.\n\nPowered By\n\n10\n\n847.2K\n\n208\n\nBarbie&apos;s Gen-Z Makeover #barbie #makeover #shorts\n\nShare\n\nNext\n\nStay\n\n14.Well, never mind,\n\n15.Even if I say that,\n\n16.I can’t help but care.\n\n17.Hey, just take a little bite,\n\n18.“Just kidding,” you say,\n\n19.Blushing like an apple.20.\n\n21.Sweeter than usual,\n\n22.The crunch overflows with the taste of love.\n\n23.Hey, I’ve realized, why is that?\n\n24.All happiness is with you, yay.25.\n\n26.Welcome back, welcome home.\n\n27.I wish I could repay you right now,\n\n28.Only here, the light shines,\n\n29.A warm place.30.\n\n31.Getting drawn into your eyes,\n\n32.I’ve never seen this before,\n\n33.In the scenery you’re seeing,\n\n34.Yes, even more excellent.35.\n\n36.Are you saying “enough already”?\n\n37.That’s not like you.\n\n38.Hey, just smile a little,\n\n39.How do you do it? Like this!\n\n40.Blushing like the color of the evening sky.41.\n\n42.It should be the same as usual,\n\n43.But my heart races,\n\n44.Hey, I’ve realized, why is that?\n\n45.I can shine only with you, yay.46.\n\n47.Gently swaying,\n\n48.Try lying down, you too.\n\n49.It’s like we’re the only two people\n\n50.In this vast world.51.\n\n52.Sweeter than usual,\n\n53.The crunch overflows with the taste of love.\n\n54.Hey, I’ve realized, why is that?\n\n55.All happiness is with you, yay.56.\n\n57.Even if I’m troubled or sad,\n\n58.The only one by my side is you.\n\n59.Hey, I’ve realized, why is that?\n\n60.I can shine only with you!61.\n\n62.Sarasarariru Sararura\n\n63.Sarasararura Sarariru\n\n[Favorite](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)\n\n[View Favorites](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/favorites/)\n\nCopy Link\n\n[](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?via=LyricalNonsense&text=%E9%9F%B3%E8%8E%89%E9%A3%B4%20%28Neriame%29%20-%20%E3%82%8A%E3%82%93%E3%81%94%E3%81%A8%E5%90%9B%20%28Ringo%20to%20Kimi%29%E3%83%BBEnglish%20TL%20%5BGlobal%5D&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyrical-nonsense.com%2Fglobal%2Flyrics%2Fneriame%2Fringo-to-kimi%2Fenglish%2F \"Twitter\")[](https://social-plugins.line.me/lineit/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyrical-nonsense.com%2Fglobal%2Flyrics%2Fneriame%2Fringo-to-kimi%2Fenglish%2F \"Line\")[](https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyrical-nonsense.com%2Fglobal%2Flyrics%2Fneriame%2Fringo-to-kimi%2Fenglish%2F \"Facebook\")[](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/ \"More\")\n\n[![Image 5: Listen on Apple Music](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/wp-content/themes/lyrical-nonsense/image/badge.svg)](https://geo.music.apple.com/jp/album/1753206193?amp;itsct=music_box_badge&itscg=30200&at=1000lrQY&app=music&ls=1 \"Listen on Apple Music\")\n\n| Romaji: | [Ringo to Kimi Lyrics (Romanized)](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/ \"Ringo to Kimi Lyrics (Romanized)\") |\n| --- |\n| Video: | [View Video](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#video) |\n\n| Artist: | [Neriame](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ \"Neriame Lyric Directory\") 音莉飴 |\n| --- |\n| Tie-in: | [Spice and Wolf: Merchant Meets the Wise Wolf](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/ookami-to-koushinryou-merchant-meets-the-wise-wolf-theme-songs/ \"Spice and Wolf: Merchant Meets the Wise Wolf Lyrics\") Ookami to Koushinryou: Merchant Meets the Wise Wolf 狼と香辛料 MERCHANT MEETS THE WISE WOLF |\n\n[Comments](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#comments)\n\n Translated by: \n\n![Image 6](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Thae-01-80.jpg)\n\n Thae Rin (星 凛) \n\nChief Editor, English Translator, Romaji Transcriber ＠ [Lyrical Nonsense](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/)\n\nJapanese music enthusiast and lyrical translator. JLPT N1 certified with more than 15 years of experience in the Japanese and Global music communities.\n\n[Join our Discord server](https://discord.gg/9QdD3cd) to connect with global music lovers\n\n[Join our team](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/about/#Recruitment) to help out + learn more about Japanese music\n\n[Send me a coffee](https://ko-fi.com/thaerin) to keep me going strong 💙\n\n (/･ω･)/ ☕彡 ヽ(^。^)ノ\n\n☕ Did we help?:[Support us with Ko-fi!](https://ko-fi.com/lyricalnonsense/)📫 Have A Request?:[Commission us here!](https://ko-fi.com/lyricalnonsense/commissions)\n\n[![Image 7: Lyrical Nonsense Discord Community](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Discord-Banner.png)](https://discord.gg/8dspgw2pBX)\n\n*   Neriame - Ringo to Kimi English Translation\n\n*   Neriame - りんごと君 English Translation\n\n*   Spice and Wolf: Merchant Meets the Wise Wolf Ending Theme 2 English Translation\n\n*   Ookami to Koushinryou: Merchant Meets the Wise Wolf Ending Theme 2 English Translation\n\n[Aa](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)[Aa](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)[Aa](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)\n\n[Left](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)[Center](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)\n\n[Dark](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)[Light](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/#)\n\n1.さらさらりる さらるら\n\n2.さらさらるら さらりる 3.\n\n4.こんにちは！\n\n5.おうちには誰かが待ってくれてる？\n\n6.お腹減るよね耳より鼻そばだてる\n\n7.そうおいしい匂いを嗅ぎ分ける 8.\n\n9.君の影を追いかけて\n\n10.届かないな改めて\n\n11.今日の気分はおしなべて\n\n12.超相当良好！！13.\n\n14.まあいっかって\n\n15.そんなん言ったって\n\n16.気になっちゃうんだもん\n\n17.ねえちょっとだけかじってみて\n\n18.なんっちゃってってなんちゃってってさ\n\n19.りんご色に染まっていく 20.\n\n21.いつもよりも甘かった\n\n22.シャクッと溢れるの恋の味\n\n23.ねえ気付いちゃったのなんでかな\n\n24.幸せは全部君となのイェイ 25.\n\n26.ただいま、おかえり。\n\n27.たった今恩返しできたら良いのになって\n\n28.ここだけがそう 明かりが灯る\n\n29.暖かい場所 30.\n\n31.君の目に吸い込まれて\n\n32.見たことなかった初めて\n\n33.君の見ている景色で\n\n34.そう、もっと上々↑35.\n\n36.もういいやって\n\n37.そんなん言っちゃうの？\n\n38.らしくないじゃん\n\n39.ねえちょっとだけ笑ってみて\n\n40.どうやってって？こうやってってさ！\n\n41.茜色に染まっていく 42.\n\n43.いつも通りのはずなのに\n\n44.ドキッと高鳴るの胸の音\n\n45.ねえ気付いちゃったのなんでかな\n\n46.輝けるのは君となのイェイ 47.\n\n48.静かに揺れる\n\n49.寝転がってみてよ 君もほら\n\n50.広い世界に2人だけみたいだね 51.\n\n52.いつもよりも甘かった\n\n53.シャクッと溢れるの恋の味\n\n54.ねえ気付いちゃったのなんでかな\n\n55.幸せは全部君となのイェイ 56.\n\n57.悩んでても悲しくても\n\n58.隣にいるのは君だけ\n\n59.気付いちゃったのなんでかな\n\n60.輝けるのは君しかいないの！61.\n\n62.さらさらりる さらるら\n\n63.さらさらるら さらりる\n\nCopy Link\n\n[](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?via=LyricalNonsense&text=%E9%9F%B3%E8%8E%89%E9%A3%B4%20%28Neriame%29%20-%20%E3%82%8A%E3%82%93%E3%81%94%E3%81%A8%E5%90%9B%20%28Ringo%20to%20Kimi%29%E3%83%BBEnglish%20TL%20%5BGlobal%5D&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyrical-nonsense.com%2Fglobal%2Flyrics%2Fneriame%2Fringo-to-kimi%2Fenglish%2F \"Twitter\")[](https://social-plugins.line.me/lineit/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyrical-nonsense.com%2Fglobal%2Flyrics%2Fneriame%2Fringo-to-kimi%2Fenglish%2F \"Line\")[](https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyrical-nonsense.com%2Fglobal%2Flyrics%2Fneriame%2Fringo-to-kimi%2Fenglish%2F \"Facebook\")[](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/english/ \"More\")\n\n[![Image 8: Listen on Apple Music](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/wp-content/themes/lyrical-nonsense/image/badge.svg)](https://geo.music.apple.com/jp/album/1753206193?amp;itsct=music_box_badge&itscg=30200&at=1000lrQY&app=music&ls=1 \"Listen on Apple Music\")\n\n| Romaji | [Ringo to Kimi Lyrics (Romanized)](https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/global/lyrics/neriame/ringo-to-kimi/ \"Ringo to Kimi Lyrics (Romanized)\") |\n| --- |\n| Video: | [View Video](https://www.lyrical-nons