{"type":"message","id":"5aab820b","parentId":"2c9a8166","timestamp":"2026-04-05T05:30:20.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nAh, buat halaman IT Support di MAGI. Makes sense — buat tampilin code snippets, config examples, command references, webhook payloads, dll.\n\nMau gue langsung integrate ke MAGI IT Support page, atau ini buat project terpisah? Kalau buat MAGI, gue bisa:\n\n1. Install code-blocks ke MAGI frontend\n2. Replace code display yang ada sekarang dengan komponen ini\n3. Add copy-to-clipboard, syntax highlighting buat JSON/bash/YAML\n\nConfirm aja approach-nya bos 👍"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":144,"cacheRead":64403,"cacheWrite":515,"totalTokens":65065,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0036000000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0322015,"cacheWrite":0.0032187500000000003,"total":0.03903525}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775367013082}}
