{"type":"message","id":"454525de","parentId":"c13e1605","timestamp":"2026-04-05T05:35:45.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All good. Here's what's live now:\n\nDone bos ✅ IT Support page udah di-upgrade:\n\n**Code Blocks (inspired by pheralb/code-blocks):**\n- 🎨 Syntax highlighting via *Sugar-High* (lightweight, no WASM, loads async dari CDN)\n- 📋 Copy-to-clipboard button (muncul on hover, animasi ✅ setelah copy)\n- 🏷️ Language badge (pill indigo — bash, json, yaml, dll)\n- 📁 Optional filename bar (kayak \"config.yaml\")\n- 🔢 Line numbers dengan separator\n- ✨ Hover glow effect yang match dark theme MAGI\n\n**Terintegrasi di:**\n- *Uriel Chat* — code blocks dari response Uriel sekarang render cantik\n- *Doctor Output* — hasil `openclaw doctor` tampil dalam styled code block\n- *Gateway Restart* — output restart juga di-wrap\n\n**Quick Commands card baru** (di bawah Emergency Panel):\n- ⚡ OpenClaw — gateway restart, status, doctor\n- 🔄 PM2 — restart, logs, list, monit\n- 🖥️ System — free, df, top, journalctl\n- 🐳 Docker — ps, stats, logs, system df\n- Tiap command ada `$` prompt + one-click copy\n\nLive di: `https://64-227-110-70.sslip.io/it-support`"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":371,"cacheRead":92393,"cacheWrite":156,"totalTokens":92921,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.009275,"cacheRead":0.046196499999999995,"cacheWrite":0.0009750000000000001,"total":0.056451499999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775367332207}}
