{"type":"message","id":"50c28674","parentId":"9f2ac953","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:05:39.396Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nTadi malam kamu kasih gue link **pheralb/code-blocks** (https://github.com/pheralb/code-blocks) — UI component library buat tampilin code snippets yang cantik.\n\nKamu bilang itu buat **IT Support page** di MAGI, dan gue langsung integrate. Yang udah live sekarang di `/it-support`:\n\n1. **Code Blocks component** — syntax highlighting pakai Sugar-High, copy button, language badge, line numbers, hover glow\n2. **Upgrade Uriel Chat** — code blocks dari response Uriel sekarang render proper (bukan `<pre>` biasa)\n3. **Doctor & Restart output** — di-wrap dalam styled code blocks\n4. **Quick Commands card** — 4 kategori (OpenClaw, PM2, System, Docker) dengan one-click copy per command\n\nSemua vanilla JS, single file, match dark theme MAGI. 👍"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":235,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":96439,"totalTokens":96677,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.005875,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.60274375,"total":0.60863375}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775369130897}}
