{"type":"message","id":"53ca3016","parentId":"5562de6d","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:10:12.652Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ULTRAPLAN launched 🧠🔥\n\nOpus lagi deep-think tentang full MAGI redesign. Dia bakal:\n\n1. **Baca semua 18 halaman** + backend + Caddy config\n2. **Analyze** setiap page, cari semua potential bugs & edge cases\n3. **Design** shared component system (tanpa build tools — tetap vanilla)\n4. **Spec** unified design system (colors, typography, spacing, components)\n5. **Plan** page-by-page redesign dengan zero-bug checklist\n6. **Split** jadi 4 parallel agent streams yang bisa di-dispatch sekaligus\n\nEstimasi selesai: **15-30 menit** tergantung seberapa banyak file yang dia baca.\n\nGue notify begitu plan ready buat review. Sit tight bos 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":215,"cacheRead":115618,"cacheWrite":2623,"totalTokens":118457,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0053750000000000004,"cacheRead":0.057809,"cacheWrite":0.016393750000000002,"total":0.07958275}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775369403864}}
