, mission (grid breaks) |\n| No back button / breadcrumb on most pages — only MAGI logo link | MEDIUM | Most pages |\n| Chat page welcome grid has 3-column layout that breaks at narrow widths | MEDIUM | chat |\n| Sidebar toggle state not persisted across page loads | LOW | chat, vault |\n| No keyboard shortcuts documented | LOW | vault (has Ctrl+S/N), others none |\n\n### 1.2 DX Issues (Developer Experience)\n| Issue | Severity | Impact |\n|-------|----------|--------|\n| Every page re-implements: CSS reset, CSS variables, font imports, body background orbs, toast system, escape function, timeAgo function, auth check | CRITICAL | ~600 lines duplicated across pages |\n| Two different CSS variable sets (dashboard uses `--bg:#0a0e1a`, most pages use `--bg:#060a14`) | HIGH | Visual inconsistency |\n| Three different markdown rendering approaches: marked.js in chat/vault, custom regex parser in roundtable, knowledge uses both | HIGH | Different rendering quality per page |\n| Auth token not checked on any page except login auto-redirect | CRITICAL | All pages accessible without login |\n| Toast implementations differ: some position fixed-top (chat), some fixed-bottom (all others) | LOW | Inconsistency |\n| Lucide icons loaded from unpkg CDN on every page — will fail offline | MEDIUM | All pages |\n\n### 1.3 Reliability Issues\n| Issue | Severity | Description |\n|-------|----------|-------------|\n| **No auth enforcement on page load** | CRITICAL | Only login page checks token. Every other page loads without authentication — APIs may fail silently |\n| **WebSocket has no heartbeat** | HIGH | Chat page does respond to `ping` from server, but if connection drops silently there's no client-side heartbeat to detect it |\n| **WebSocket reconnect is naive** | HIGH | Chat page just does `setTimeout(connectWS, 3000)` — no exponential backoff, no max retries, no user notification of repeated failure |\n| **No 401 handling on API calls** | CRITICAL | If token expires, fetch calls return errors but pages don't redirect to login |\n| **Memory leaks in monitor page** | HIGH | `setInterval(loadAll, 30000)` never cleared, Lucide icons re-created on every refresh |\n| **Memory leaks in notifications** | MEDIUM | Same 30s interval, never cleared |\n| **Roundtable stores history in localStorage** | MEDIUM | localStorage has 5-10MB limit; 50 full roundtable conversations could exceed this |\n| **XSS in roundtable** | HIGH | Custom markdown renderer doesn't escape HTML: `renderMarkdown()` function is regex-based, no sanitization |\n| **No error boundaries** | HIGH | A single JS error in rendering kills the entire page |\n\n…(truncated)…"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775369451277,"__openclaw":{"id":"c1c0d7f8","seq":30}}],"truncated":true,"droppedMessages":false,"contentTruncated":true,"contentRedacted":false,"bytes":4865},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775369705457}}
