{"type":"message","id":"c23df344","parentId":"39ef29f0","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:15:35.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK Lucy, ULTRAPLAN complete. Here's the verdict:\n\n---\n\n**🏗️ MAGI Redesign Plan — Executive Summary**\n\nOpus baca SEMUA 18 halaman + backend + Caddy config. Kesimpulan: *\"Visually impressive but structurally fragile.\"* Theme-nya cantik, tapi arsitekturnya house of cards.\n\n---\n\n**🚨 CRITICAL BUGS Found:**\n\n1. **No auth enforcement** — semua page bisa diakses TANPA login. API calls fail silently\n2. **XSS vulnerability** di Roundtable — markdown renderer nggak escape HTML\n3. **No 401 handling** — kalau token expired, halaman nggak redirect ke login\n4. **Memory leaks** — monitor & notifications pakai `setInterval` yang nggak pernah di-clear\n5. **WebSocket reconnect naive** — no backoff, no max retries, no user notification\n6. **~600 lines duplicated** across pages — CSS reset, variables, fonts, toast, auth check\n\n**📐 Architecture Decision: Vanilla ES Modules (No Build Tools)**\n\nExtract shared infrastructure ke `/shared/`:\n- `core.css` — unified design tokens (satu source of truth)\n- `components.css` — buttons, cards, inputs, modals, toasts\n- `core.js` — auth guard, API client, toast, escape, timeAgo\n- `ws-manager.js` — WebSocket with reconnect + heartbeat\n- `markdown.js` — shared renderer (XSS-safe)\n- `nav.js` — global navigation\n\nZero build tools. Tetap vanilla. ES modules native di browser.\n\n**🎨 Design System Fix:**\nSekarang ada 5 VERSI BEDA CSS variables di halaman berbeda. Chat punya primary/accent KEBALIK dari dashboard. Plan: satu unified set.\n\n**📱 Mobile Issues:**\n- Leads sidebar nggak collapse\n- Roundtable sidebar jadi strip\n- Mission grid breaks\n- Touch targets terlalu kecil\n\n**4 Agent Parallel Execution Plan:**\n- *Agent 1:* Shared infrastructure (core.css, core.js, nav, auth guard)\n- *Agent 2:* Core pages (chat, vault, roundtable, knowledge)\n- *Agent 3:* Operations pages (settings, monitor, analytics, tasks, files, mission)\n- *Agent 4:* Business pages (leads, icat, pipeline, broadcast, notifications, reports, login, dashboard)\n\n---\n\nMau gue:\n1. **Approve & dispatch 4 agent sekarang?** \n2. **Review plan lebih detail dulu?** (gue bisa visual-explain buat breakdown per page)\n3. **Modify** — ada yang mau ditambah/ubah?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":678,"cacheRead":144015,"cacheWrite":286,"totalTokens":144980,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.01695,"cacheRead":0.0720075,"cacheWrite":0.0017875,"total":0.09075}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775369717445}}
