{"type":"message","id":"d9d3da52","parentId":"e8637734","timestamp":"2026-04-05T07:53:11.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke, dispatching 4 agents sekarang! 🚀\n\nGue mulai dari **Agent 1: Shared Infrastructure** dulu — karena Agent 2, 3, 4 depend on this."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_FwWhRMaXDoGQKlTI3bvlcv","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"magi-agent1-shared-infra","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":900,"task":"# MAGI Redesign — Agent 1: Shared Infrastructure\n\nYou are building the shared foundation that ALL other MAGI pages will import. This MUST be done first and MUST be bulletproof.\n\n## Context\nMAGI is a web dashboard at ~/magi-v2/frontend/ with 18 self-contained HTML pages. Currently each page re-implements CSS reset, variables, fonts, toast, auth check, etc (~600 lines duplicated). We're extracting shared infrastructure into ES modules.\n\n## Your Deliverables\n\n### 1. `/shared/core.css` — Unified Design System\nCreate a single CSS file with:\n\n**CSS Reset + Base:**\n```css\n*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0 }\nhtml, body { height: 100% }\nbody { font-family: var(--font-sans); background: var(--bg-base); color: var(--text-primary); }\n```\n\n**CSS Variables (ONE source of truth):**\n```css\n:root {\n  --bg-base: #060a14;\n  --bg-elevated: #0c1020;\n  --bg-surface: rgba(12, 17, 30, 0.92);\n  --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);\n  --glass-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);\n  --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);\n  --glass-border-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);\n  --text-primary: #e8edf5;\n  --text-secondary: #8b95a8;\n  --text-tertiary: #5a6478;\n  --text-muted: #2e3b55;\n  --color-primary: #818cf8;\n  --color-primary-dim: rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.12);\n  --color-accent: #34d399;\n  --color-accent-dim: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.12);\n  --color-success: #34d399;\n  --color-warning: #fbbf24;\n  --color-danger: #f87171;\n  --color-info: #60a5fa;\n  --radius-sm: 6px; --radius-md: 10px; --radius-lg: 14px;\n  --font-sans: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;\n  --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', monospace;\n  --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);\n  --duration-fast: 150ms; --duration-normal: 200ms;\n}\n```\n\n**Background ambient orbs** (currently duplicated on every page):\n```css\nbody::before, body::after { content:''; position:fixed; pointer-events:none; z-index:0; }\nbody::before { top:-200px;left:-100px;width:600px;height:600px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(99,102,241,.06),transparent 70%); }\nbody::after { bottom:-200px;right:-100px;width:700px;height:700px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(52,211,153,.04),transparent 70%); }\n```\n\n**Scrollbar styling, selection color, font-face declarations** for Inter weights (reference ~/magi-v2/frontend/shared/fonts/).\n\n### 2. `/shared/components.css` — Reusable Components\nCSS-only components:\n- `.btn`, `.btn-primary`, `.btn-danger`, `.btn-ghost`, `.btn-sm`, `.btn-lg`, `.btn-icon`\n- `.card`, `.card-header`, `.card-body` (glass morphism)\n- `.input`, `.select`, `.textarea`, `.input-group`\n- `.badge`, `.badge-success`, `.badge-warning`, `.badge-danger`\n- `.modal-overlay`, `.modal`, `.modal-header`, `.modal-body`, `.modal-footer`\n- `.toast` (positioned fixed bottom-right)\n- `.table`, `.table-row`\n- `.spinner` (CSS-only loading spinner)\n- `.empty-state` (icon + text + optional action)\n- `.page-layout` (full-height flex with optional sidebar)\n- `.sidebar`, `.sidebar-item`, `.sidebar-item.active`\n- `.topbar` (sticky top with glass effect)\n\nStyle all components to match the existing glass-morphism dark theme. Look at ~/magi-v2/frontend/chat/index.html and ~/magi-v2/frontend/settings/index.html for reference.\n\n### 3. `/shared/core.js` — ES Module with shared utilities\n\n```javascript\n// Auth guard — check token, redirect to /login/ if missing/expired\nexport function authGuard() { ... }\n\n// API client — fetch wrapper with auth header, 401 redirect, error handling\nexport async function api(path, options = {}) { ... }\n\n// Toast system\nexport function toast(message, type = 'info', duration = 4000) { ... }\n\n// Utility functions\nexport function escHtml(str) { ... }\nexport function timeAgo(date) { ... }\nexport function formatNumber(n) { ... }\nexport function debounce(fn, ms) { ... }\n\n// Loading state helper\nexport function setLoading(element, loading) { ... }\n\n// Init function — call on every page\nexport function initPage() { ... } // runs authGuard, injects toast container, sets up global error handler\n```\n\n**Auth guard details:**\n- Read token from localStorage('magi_token')\n- Check /api/auth/me to validate\n- If 401 or no token → redirect to /login/\n- Add global fetch interceptor: any 401 response → redirect to /login/\n\n**API client details:**\n- Prepend /api/ if path doesn't start with /\n- Add Authorization header with token\n- Parse JSON response\n- On 401 → authGuard redirect\n- On network error → toast error message\n- Return { data, error } tuple\n\n### 4. `/shared/nav.js` — Global Navigation Component\n\nRender a collapsible sidebar navigation that appears on ALL pages:\n\n```javascript\nexport function renderNav(activePage) { ... }\n```\n\nNavigation items (grouped):\n- **Core:** Dashboard, Chat, Roundtable, Vault\n- **Operations:** Mission Control, Monitor, Analytics, Tasks, Files\n- **Business:** Leads, ICat, Pipeline, Broadcast\n- **System:** Settings, Reports, Notifications\n\nMobile: hamburger menu → slide-out overlay sidebar\nDesktop: thin icon sidebar (expandable on hover to show labels)\n\nThe nav should be injected into a `<div id=\"nav\"></div>` at the top of each page's body.\n\n### 5. `/shared/ws-manager.js` — WebSocket Manager\n\n```javascript\nexport class WSManager {\n  constructor(url, options = {}) { ... }\n  connect() { ... }\n  disconnect() { ... }\n  send(data) { ... }\n  on(event, handler) { ... }\n  off(event, handler) { ... }\n}\n```\n\nFeatures:\n- Exponential backoff reconnect (1s → 2s → 4s → 8s → max 30s)\n- Max retry limit (default 20) with user notification\n- Client-side heartbeat ping every 30s\n- Connection state events: 'open', 'close', 'error', 'reconnecting', 'max-retries'\n- Message events: 'message'\n- Visual connection indicator (green dot / red dot / yellow reconnecting)\n\n### 6. `/shared/markdown.js` — Safe Markdown Renderer\n\n```javascript\nexport function renderMarkdown(text) { ... }\n```\n\n- Use the existing /shared/marked.min.js + /shared/highlight.min.js\n- ADD XSS sanitization (escape HTML before rendering, or use DOMPurify-style sanitizer)\n- Consistent rendering across all pages\n- Support: bold, italic, code, code blocks with syntax highlighting, lists, links, tables, blockquotes\n\n## Rules\n- Read existing pages first to understand current patterns\n- All files go in ~/magi-v2/frontend/shared/\n- Do NOT modify any existing page files (other agents will do that)\n- Test that ES module imports work: `<script type=\"module\">import { initPage } from '/shared/core.js';</script>`\n- Keep file sizes reasonable (core.css < 300 lines, components.css < 400 lines, core.js < 200 lines)\n- Self-host everything — no CDN dependencies except Google Fonts fallback\n- Make sure the toast container is injected via JS, not hardcoded in HTML\n\n## Files to Read First\n- ~/magi-v2/frontend/chat/index.html (most complex, best reference for glass theme)\n- ~/magi-v2/frontend/settings/index.html (component patterns)\n- ~/magi-v2/frontend/monitor/index.html (card patterns)\n- ~/magi-v2/frontend/shared/ (existing shared assets)\n- ~/magi-v2/frontend/login/index.html (auth flow)"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":2406,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":149739,"totalTokens":152148,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.06015,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.93586875,"total":0.99603375}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775375538792}}
