{"type":"message","id":"f11caa1a","parentId":"848ef3b1","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:02:39.300Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_4xqYS7WPjAtIxHwNKKUpVf","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"magi-agent3-ops-pages","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":900,"task":"# MAGI Redesign — Agent 3: Operations Pages (Settings, Monitor, Analytics, Tasks, Files, Mission)\n\nYou are migrating 6 operations pages to use the new shared infrastructure.\n\n## Shared Infrastructure (already built at ~/magi-v2/frontend/shared/)\nImport these in each page:\n```html\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/shared/core.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/shared/components.css\">\n<script type=\"module\">\nimport { initPage, api, toast, escHtml, timeAgo, setLoading, formatNumber } from '/shared/core.js';\nimport { renderNav } from '/shared/nav.js';\n\ninitPage();\nrenderNav('settings'); // or 'monitor', 'analytics', 'tasks', 'files', 'mission'\n</script>\n```\n\n## Your 6 Pages\n\n### 1. Settings (~/magi-v2/frontend/settings/index.html) — 970 lines (LARGEST)\n**Currently:** Agent models, intensity, users, channels, cron jobs. Complex with many tabs.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace ALL inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Remove duplicated reset, variables, fonts, toast, utilities\n- Add loading states for each settings section\n- Add error handling for save operations\n- Fix: uses both `/api/` and `/council-api/` — standardize to use shared `api()` function\n- Keep: all tab functionality, model selectors, intensity controls\n\n### 2. Monitor (~/magi-v2/frontend/monitor/index.html) — 341 lines\n**Currently:** Agent status grid, channel routing, activity log.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- CRITICAL FIX: Memory leak — `setInterval(loadAll, 30000)` never cleared, Lucide icons re-created every refresh → clear interval on page unload, reuse icon instances\n- Add loading states for agent grid\n- Add error handling for API calls\n- Keep: agent cards, status indicators, routing display\n\n### 3. Analytics (~/magi-v2/frontend/analytics/index.html) — 412 lines\n**Currently:** Usage stats, tokens, costs, system health.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Add loading states for chart data\n- Add error states for failed API calls\n- Add empty state for no data\n- Keep: charts, stat cards, time filters\n\n### 4. Tasks (~/magi-v2/frontend/tasks/index.html) — 354 lines\n**Currently:** Kanban board with columns.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Add empty state (\"No tasks yet — create your first task\")\n- Add loading states\n- Add error handling\n- Keep: kanban columns, task cards, create/edit/delete\n\n### 5. Files (~/magi-v2/frontend/files/index.html) — 334 lines\n**Currently:** VPS file manager with breadcrumbs, upload, download.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Add loading states for directory listing\n- Add error handling (permission denied, file not found)\n- Add empty state for empty directories\n- Keep: breadcrumbs, file list, upload, download, edit, disk info\n\n### 6. Mission Control (~/magi-v2/frontend/mission/index.html) — 343 lines\n**Currently:** Real-time system overview with agent status, services, resources.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Fix: grid layout breaks on mobile → stack cards vertically\n- Add loading states\n- Add error handling\n- Keep: overview cards, agent status, resource monitors\n\n## Rules\n- Read each page's FULL current code first before modifying\n- Read the shared files at ~/magi-v2/frontend/shared/ (core.css, components.css, core.js, nav.js) to understand what's available\n- Keep ALL existing functionality\n- Visual look stays the same — glass-morphism dark theme with shared tokens\n- Remove all duplicated code now in shared modules\n- Each page should be shorter after migration\n- Add `<div id=\"nav\"></div>` as first child of body\n- All `<script>` using imports must be `type=\"module\"`\n- Every API call → shared `api()` function\n- Every toast → shared `toast()` function\n- Add loading states for ALL async operations\n- Add error handling for ALL API calls\n- Mobile responsive: consider 320px-1920px\n- For the memory leak in monitor: use `window.addEventListener('beforeunload', () => clearInterval(refreshTimer))` or similar"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":1236,"cacheRead":150931,"cacheWrite":1693,"totalTokens":153861,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0309,"cacheRead":0.07546549999999999,"cacheWrite":0.01058125,"total":0.11695175}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775376136131}}
