{"type":"message","id":"ce026653","parentId":"3bbfc9e0","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:03:08.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_Nz0bn4AE1ke5Y5ho9fTS6A","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"magi-agent4-biz-pages","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":900,"task":"# MAGI Redesign — Agent 4: Business & System Pages (Leads, ICat, Pipeline, Broadcast, Notifications, Reports, Login, Dashboard)\n\nYou are migrating 8 pages to use the new shared infrastructure.\n\n## Shared Infrastructure (already built at ~/magi-v2/frontend/shared/)\nImport these in each page:\n```html\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/shared/core.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/shared/components.css\">\n<script type=\"module\">\nimport { initPage, api, toast, escHtml, timeAgo, setLoading, formatNumber } from '/shared/core.js';\nimport { renderNav } from '/shared/nav.js';\n\ninitPage();\nrenderNav('leads'); // or appropriate page name\n</script>\n```\n\n## Your 8 Pages\n\n### 1. Dashboard (~/magi-v2/frontend/dashboard/index.html) — 241 lines\n**Currently:** App launcher with cards linking to sub-apps. MAGI logo, status pill.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard (initPage)\n- Add global nav via renderNav('dashboard')\n- Keep: app launcher cards, MAGI gradient logo, status indicator\n- This is the LANDING PAGE — should feel premium\n- Don't add sidebar nav here, just a minimal topbar with settings/logout\n- ACTUALLY: add the full nav sidebar. Dashboard becomes the home view within the nav structure.\n\n### 2. Login (~/magi-v2/frontend/login/index.html) — 71 lines\n**Currently:** Simple login form.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports (core.css, components.css)\n- Do NOT add auth guard (this IS the auth page)\n- Do NOT add global nav (pre-auth page)\n- Add: loading state on login button while authenticating\n- Add: error message display for wrong credentials\n- Add: password visibility toggle\n- Keep: centered card layout, MAGI branding\n- After successful login → redirect to /dashboard/\n\n### 3. Leads (~/magi-v2/frontend/leads/index.html) — 668 lines\n**Currently:** 158K business leads with map, filters, tiers, chart.js, export.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Fix: sidebar won't collapse on mobile → proper toggle\n- Add loading states for lead list and map\n- Add error handling\n- Keep: map (Leaflet), chart.js, filters, tier system, export\n- Performance: lazy-load Leaflet and Chart.js only when needed\n\n### 4. ICat (~/magi-v2/frontend/icat/index.html) — 494 lines\n**Currently:** Contact manager, message templates, auto-reply rules.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Add loading states for contacts list\n- Add empty states (\"No contacts yet\", \"No templates yet\")\n- Add error handling\n- Keep: tabs (contacts, templates, rules), CRUD operations\n\n### 5. Pipeline (~/magi-v2/frontend/pipeline/index.html) — 160 lines\n**Currently:** Sales funnel — track deals from lead to close. (relatively small)\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Add empty state (\"No deals in pipeline\")\n- Add loading states\n- Keep: pipeline stages, deal cards\n\n### 6. Broadcast (~/magi-v2/frontend/broadcast/index.html) — 135 lines\n**Currently:** Bulk messaging with templates and rate limiting.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Add loading/sending states\n- Add error handling\n- Keep: template selector, recipient list, send controls\n\n### 7. Notifications (~/magi-v2/frontend/notifications/index.html) — 83 lines\n**Currently:** Central inbox for alerts. Very minimal.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- CRITICAL FIX: Memory leak — setInterval never cleared → add cleanup\n- Add empty state (\"No notifications\")\n- Add loading state\n- Add mark-all-as-read\n- Keep: notification list, read/unread states\n\n### 8. Reports (~/magi-v2/frontend/reports/index.html) — 120 lines\n**Currently:** Weekly summaries, agent performance, cost breakdown.\n**Changes needed:**\n- Replace inline CSS with shared imports\n- Add auth guard + global nav\n- Add loading states\n- Add empty state (\"No reports generated yet\")\n- Add error handling\n- Keep: report list, detail view\n\n## Rules\n- Read each page's FULL current code first before modifying\n- Read the shared files at ~/magi-v2/frontend/shared/ (core.css, components.css, core.js, nav.js) to understand what's available\n- Keep ALL existing functionality\n- Visual look stays the same — glass-morphism dark theme with shared tokens\n- Remove all duplicated code now in shared modules\n- Each page should be shorter after migration\n- Add `<div id=\"nav\"></div>` as first child of body (EXCEPT login page)\n- All `<script>` using imports must be `type=\"module\"`\n- Every API call → shared `api()` function\n- Every toast → shared `toast()` function\n- Add loading states for ALL async operations\n- Add error handling for ALL API calls\n- Mobile responsive: consider 320px-1920px\n- Login page: no nav, no auth guard, centered design\n- Dashboard: full nav sidebar, premium feel"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":1445,"cacheRead":152624,"cacheWrite":1433,"totalTokens":155503,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.036125000000000004,"cacheRead":0.07631199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00895625,"total":0.12139824999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775376159951}}
