{"type":"message","id":"cc2607b3","parentId":"dc719976","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:18:15.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 6 ops pages migrated successfully!\n\n**Agent 3 DONE** ✅ — 6 Operations Pages migrated!\n\n- *Settings:* 970→866 lines, auth guard, nav, shared API client\n- *Monitor:* 341→337 lines, **memory leak FIXED** (clearInterval + visibility cleanup)\n- *Analytics:* 412→392 lines, auth guard, nav, loading states\n- *Tasks:* 354→337 lines, auth guard, nav, empty states\n- *Files:* 334→428 lines (added loading/error handling), keeps FormData for uploads\n- *Mission:* 343→367 lines, auth guard, nav, mobile grid fix\n\n---\n\n🎉 **ALL 4 AGENTS COMPLETE!**\n\n**Final Scorecard:**\n- ✅ Agent 1: 6 shared infrastructure files\n- ✅ Agent 2: 4 core pages (chat, vault, roundtable, knowledge)\n- ✅ Agent 3: 6 ops pages (settings, monitor, analytics, tasks, files, mission)\n- ✅ Agent 4: 8 biz pages (dashboard, login, leads, icat, pipeline, broadcast, notifications, reports)\n\n**18 pages migrated. Bugs fixed:**\n- 🔒 Auth guard on ALL pages\n- 🛡️ XSS vulnerability in Roundtable — FIXED\n- 🧹 Memory leaks in Monitor & Notifications — FIXED\n- 📱 Mobile responsive improvements\n- ⚡ Lazy-loading for Leaflet, Chart.js\n- 🔌 WebSocket reconnect with exponential backoff\n- 📋 Loading states & error handling everywhere\n- 🎨 Unified CSS variables (one source of truth)\n\nMau gue test sekarang di browser, atau kamu mau cek langsung di `magi.64-227-110-70.sslip.io`?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":473,"cacheRead":160218,"cacheWrite":119,"totalTokens":160811,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.011825,"cacheRead":0.080109,"cacheWrite":0.00074375,"total":0.09268275}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775377083368}}
