{"type":"message","id":"57ed868c","parentId":"6d368603","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:43:29.725Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**AlphaClaw Apex** 🐺 — native Mac app buat manage MULTIPLE OpenClaw VPS instances dari satu dashboard.\n\nIni level up dari AlphaClaw biasa. Basically:\n\n**Target user:** Orang yang setup OpenClaw buat *clients* as a service. Managed OpenClaw provider.\n\n**Key features:**\n- 🖥️ Deploy ke Hetzner VPS in one click\n- 📊 Monitor ALL instances dari satu UI\n- 🩺 *Drift Doctor* — analyzes prompts & workspace buat detect agent drift (baru!)\n- 🐕 Per-instance watchdog + crash recovery\n- 📂 Full file browser, editor, terminal — no SSH\n- 🪝 Webhook creator & inspector with *replay & debug*\n- ⬆️ One-click updates, no redeploy\n- 📦 Import existing setup from GitHub\n- Semua fitur AlphaClaw web, tapi native Mac app + multi-instance\n\n**Relevan buat kita?**\n\nHonestly — *not directly*. Kita cuma punya 1 VPS, bukan managed service. Tapi ada 2 hal yang menarik buat di-steal:\n\n1. **Drift Doctor** — concept bagus. Analyze apakah agent prompts sudah \"drift\" dari intended behavior. Kita bisa bikin versi sederhana di MAGI.\n\n2. **Webhook inspector with replay** — kalau kita nanti integrate webhook buat DataFlow (invoice OCR callbacks dll), ini priceless.\n\nIni lebih ke \"interesting to watch\" buat sekarang. Kalau Lucy nanti mau jual managed AI services lewat Sentra, Apex jadi sangat relevant.\n\nMau gue explore lebih dalam salah satu fiturnya?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":445,"cacheRead":164694,"cacheWrite":1663,"totalTokens":166803,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.011125000000000001,"cacheRead":0.08234699999999999,"cacheWrite":0.01039375,"total":0.10387074999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775378597176}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f06870c","parentId":"57ed868c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:44:47.053Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"AC39AC38DD2E37D750AFACF7035881A2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nkamu bisa liat videonya?"}],"timestamp":1775378687016}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca7e05d7","parentId":"7f06870c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:44:55.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNggak bisa bos — video di Twitter/X nggak bisa gue extract. Yang gue dapet cuma thumbnail image dan text tweet-nya. Twitter embed video butuh authentication + JS rendering yang di-block.\n\nKalau kamu mau gue liat UI-nya, bisa:\n1. **Screenshot** beberapa frame menarik → kirim ke sini\n2. **Screen record** → kirim sebagai video, gue bisa extract frames\n\nAtau kalau ada specific feature dari video yang mau gue replicate buat MAGI, describe aja — gue build based on description kamu 👍"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":153,"cacheRead":166357,"cacheWrite":607,"totalTokens":167120,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0038250000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0831785,"cacheWrite":0.0037937500000000002,"total":0.09081225}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775378687042}}
{"type":"message","id":"dfcab49c","parentId":"ca7e05d7","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:47:14.557Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/ac68cf38-d1fa-42bd-b719-5e8aa29d97c0.mp4 (video/mp4)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"AC87251EB08D07D25EFD0ED10D3879B0\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nI like the animation and the UI , and I want to make MAGI with this UI UX Reference"}],"timestamp":1775378834517}}
{"type":"message","id":"48b96fb6","parentId":"dfcab49c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:47:19.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nLet me extract frames from this video to study the UI/UX patterns."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_gwQxd9Om4vObTefEQ6nJ2m","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-frames/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":86,"cacheRead":166964,"cacheWrite":471,"totalTokens":167524,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.00215,"cacheRead":0.083482,"cacheWrite":0.00294375,"total":0.08859075}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775378834548}}
{"type":"message","id":"85393d88","parentId":"48b96fb6","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:47:19.373Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_gwQxd9Om4vObTefEQ6nJ2m","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: video-frames\ndescription: Extract frames or short clips from videos using ffmpeg.\nhomepage: https://ffmpeg.org\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"🎞️\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"ffmpeg\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"ffmpeg\",\n              \"bins\": [\"ffmpeg\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ffmpeg (brew)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Video Frames (ffmpeg)\n\nExtract a single frame from a video, or create quick thumbnails for inspection.\n\n## Quick start\n\nFirst frame:\n\n```bash\n{baseDir}/scripts/frame.sh /path/to/video.mp4 --out /tmp/frame.jpg\n```\n\nAt a timestamp:\n\n```bash\n{baseDir}/scripts/frame.sh /path/to/video.mp4 --time 00:00:10 --out /tmp/frame-10s.jpg\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- Prefer `--time` for “what is happening around here?”.\n- Use a `.jpg` for quick share; use `.png` for crisp UI frames.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775378839359}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb6ea13f","parentId":"85393d88","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:47:25.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_JEMpcnC9ZkSINzWnp5wfMG","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Get video info first\nffprobe -v quiet -print_format json -show_format -show_streams /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/ac68cf38-d1fa-42bd-b719-5e8aa29d97c0.mp4 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); f=d.get('format',{}); print(f'Duration: {f.get(\\\"duration\\\",\\\"?\\\")}s'); [print(f'Stream: {s[\\\"codec_type\\\"]} {s.get(\\\"width\\\",\\\"\\\")}x{s.get(\\\"height\\\",\\\"\\\")} {s.get(\\\"codec_name\\\",\\\"\\\")}') for s in d.get('streams',[])]\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":260,"cacheRead":167435,"cacheWrite":400,"totalTokens":168096,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.006500000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0837175,"cacheWrite":0.0025,"total":0.0927225}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775378839382}}
