n- ✅ Apex token swap in `:root`\n- ✅ Grid texture background, JetBrains Mono font\n- ✅ Login box accent: cyan\n- ✅ All indigo references converted to cyan\n- ✅ Refresh buttons, badges, scrollbars: cyan\n- ✅ Added inline Apex sidebar nav\n- ✅ JS agent colors preserved (data, not theme)\n\n### Paul Simulator — D&D App (Amber/Gold Accent #d4a73a)\n\n**4. Main D&D App (`index.html` + `styles.css`)**\n- ✅ Updated `styles.css` `:root` tokens: `--bg-base:#0d121b`, `--bg-surface:#0f141f`, `--bg-card:#0f1521`, `--gold:#d4a73a`, `--gold-dim:#b8922e`, `--text:#c9d1d9`\n- ✅ Body font: JetBrains Mono 13px with `padding-left:56px`\n- ✅ Added `body::before` grid texture\n- ✅ Amber selection highlight\n- ✅ Scrollbar: amber thumb\n- ✅ All `rgba(245,158,11,...)` → `rgba(212,167,58,...)`\n- ✅ All `#F59E0B` → `#d4a73a`, `#D97706` → `#b8922e`\n- ✅ Added JetBrains Mono to font link\n- ✅ Added inline Apex sidebar nav (amber accent, links to MAGI Dashboard, D&D Main, Guide, Flow)\n- ✅ Used `nav-item-link` class to avoid conflict with app's internal `nav-btn` sidebar\n- ✅ Cinzel font kept for headings (fantasy flavor)\n\n**5. D&D Guide (`guide.html`)**\n- ✅ Apex token swap in `:root`\n- ✅ Body: JetBrains Mono, grid texture, `padding-left:56px`\n- ✅ All amber/gold refs updated to `#d4a73a`\n- ✅ Top bar background updated\n- ✅ Hero gradient updated\n- ✅ Button font updated to JetBrains Mono\n- ✅ Added inline Apex sidebar nav (amber accent)\n\n**6. D&D Flow (`flow.html`)**\n- ✅ Apex token swap in `:root` (`--bg:#0d121b`, `--surface:#0f141f`, `--text:#c9d1d9`)\n- ✅ Body: JetBrains Mono 13px, grid texture\n- ✅ Replaced gradient orb with full-screen grid texture\n- ✅ `--font-body` changed from DM Sans to JetBrains Mono\n- ✅ Added inline Apex sidebar nav (amber accent)\n\n### Sidebar Pattern (All 6 pages)\n- 56px collapsed, 200px expanded on hover\n- MAGI sun SVG logo with accent color\n- Nav items: active state with left border accent color\n- Mobile (<768px): hidden by default, hamburger button toggles\n- Council pages: cyan accent links\n- D&D pages: amber accent links, `nav-item-link` class to avoid D&D internal nav conflicts\n\n### Preserved\n- ✅ All JavaScript functionality intact (no JS changes)\n- ✅ D&D Cinzel font kept for fantasy headings\n- ✅ D&D light theme CSS preserved\n- ✅ All HTML structure balanced (`<body>`/`</body>`, `<html>`/`</html>`, `<script>`/`</script>`)\n- ✅ Agent color data in JS preserved (not theme colors)\n<<<END_UNTRUSTED_CHILD_RESULT>>>\n\nStats: runtime 9m48s • tokens 29.3k (in 71 / out 29.2k) • prompt/cache 130.5k\n\nAction:\nA completed subagent task is ready for user delivery. Convert the result above into your normal assistant voice and send that user-facing update now. Keep this internal context private (don't mention system/log/stats/session details or announce type)."}],"timestamp":1775381295190,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:cb0516e3-a7f4-46ec-a0a2-79768e786a36","sourceChannel":"webchat","sourceTool":"subagent_announce"}}}
