{"type":"message","id":"ad30a3cf","parentId":"ee739f28","timestamp":"2026-04-05T09:47:01.396Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nSekarang belum ada bedanya — role masih label doang, belum di-enforce di backend. Mau gue implement permission system-nya?\n\nIni rencana gue:\n\n**Admin** (richard, lucy)\n- Full access semua fitur\n- Manage users (approve/reject/delete/change role)\n- Settings, agent models, system controls\n- Chat, Roundtable, semua page\n\n**Editor**\n- Chat + Roundtable (bisa kirim message)\n- Vault (bisa create/edit notes)\n- Tasks (bisa create/edit)\n- Knowledge Base (read + create)\n- NGGAK bisa: Settings, User Management, Monitor, Analytics, agent model changes\n\n**Viewer**\n- Read-only semua page\n- Bisa lihat chat history tapi NGGAK bisa kirim message\n- Bisa lihat vault notes tapi NGGAK bisa edit\n- Bisa lihat tasks tapi NGGAK bisa create/edit\n- NGGAK bisa: Settings, User Management, file upload/delete\n\nBasically: Admin = full control, Editor = bisa interact, Viewer = lihat doang.\n\nMau gue apply sekarang, atau kamu mau adjust permission-nya?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":306,"cacheRead":27263,"cacheWrite":212433,"totalTokens":240005,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0076500000000000005,"cacheRead":0.0136315,"cacheWrite":1.32770625,"total":1.3490027500000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775382407668}}
