{"type":"message","id":"c80ad0f1","parentId":"d4d01315","timestamp":"2026-04-05T12:34:30.421Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_0I5q03Ix3nAJKWWHYeoIv0","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Phantom Sage - Silence (Ft. Byndy) - Lyrics - YouListener.com\nURL: https://www.youlistener.com/lyrics/phantom-sage-silence-ft-byndy\n[Verse] The silence calls to me. From the treetops of this world. A balance I'm feeling free. I'm a part of this place unfurled [Refrain]\n\n## SILENCE (FEAT. BYNDY) - Phantom Sage - LETRAS.COM\nURL: https://www.letras.com/phantom-sage/silence-feat-byndy/\nSilence (feat. Byndy). The silence. Calls to me from the. Treetops of this world. A balance. I'm feeling free. I'm a part of this place. Unfurled And I know\n\n## Silence - song and lyrics by Phantom Sage, Byndy - Spotify\nURL: https://open.spotify.com/track/0H3evvgCjc69N9RI9KJpUV"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1061,"aggregated":"## Phantom Sage - Silence (Ft. Byndy) - Lyrics - YouListener.com\nURL: https://www.youlistener.com/lyrics/phantom-sage-silence-ft-byndy\n[Verse] The silence calls to me. From the treetops of this world. A balance I'm feeling free. I'm a part of this place unfurled [Refrain]\n\n## SILENCE (FEAT. BYNDY) - Phantom Sage - LETRAS.COM\nURL: https://www.letras.com/phantom-sage/silence-feat-byndy/\nSilence (feat. Byndy). The silence. Calls to me from the. Treetops of this world. A balance. I'm feeling free. I'm a part of this place. Unfurled And I know\n\n## Silence - song and lyrics by Phantom Sage, Byndy - Spotify\nURL: https://open.spotify.com/track/0H3evvgCjc69N9RI9KJpUV","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775392470389}}
