{"type":"message","id":"537990c3","parentId":"1d0f8f6b","timestamp":"2026-04-05T12:38:39.270Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_e0yTsFN3kQX0eKWhFPUOcb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-05\n\n## 04:00-06:00 — Code-Blocks Integration + Rusdi Song Analysis\n- Integrated pheralb/code-blocks into IT Support page (Sugar-High syntax highlighter, copy buttons, language badges, line numbers)\n- Added Quick Commands card (OpenClaw, PM2, System, Docker)\n- Analyzed Ringo Biyori (Spice & Wolf ED1) and Ringo to Kimi (ED2 2024 remake) in deep detail for Rusdi\n\n## 06:00-06:15 — ULTRAPLAN #1: MAGI Redesign\n- Lucy requested full MAGI web app redesign with zero bugs\n- ULTRAPLAN Opus session analyzed all 18 pages + backend + Caddy\n- Found: no auth enforcement, XSS in roundtable, memory leaks, ~600 lines duplicated, 5 different CSS variable sets\n- Decision: Vanilla ES Modules (no build tools) — extract shared infrastructure\n\n## 06:15-06:30 — AlphaClaw Discovery\n- Lucy shared https://github.com/chrysb/alphaclaw — OpenClaw setup harness\n- Also shared AlphaClaw Apex tweet (native Mac app for fleet management)\n- Extracted video frames (65s demo) — analyzed full UI/UX design language\n\n## 07:45-08:20 — MAGI Migration Wave 1 (4 parallel agents)\n- Agent 1: Shared infra (core.css, components.css, core.js, nav.js, ws-manager.js, markdown.js)\n- Agent 2: 4 core pages (chat, vault, roundtable, knowledge) — auth guard, shared markdown, XSS fix\n- Agent 3: 6 ops pages (settings, monitor, analytics, tasks, files, mission) — memory leak fixes\n- Agent 4: 8 biz pages (dashboard, login, leads, icat, pipeline, broadcast, notifications, reports)\nALL COMPLETED ✅\n\n## 08:45-09:30 — ULTRAPLAN #2 + APEX Visual Overhaul (4 parallel agents)\n- Lucy sent AlphaClaw Apex video, wants that UI/UX style\n- ULTRAPLAN #2: full visual redesign spec (Apex tokens, transitions, stagger animations)\n- Agent 1: Shared infra overhaul (cyan accent, JetBrains Mono