{"type":"message","id":"988b1aeb","parentId":"b5834f95","timestamp":"2026-04-05T12:52:32.976Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/5dc1c0a1-5f3e-4263-b017-20ba1c615344.jpg (image/jpeg)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"ACD2195D584847E05A9F1402AAFCCE69\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nak mau ini g harus ak landscape , burger hanya untuk ke landing page , gimana caranya ak bisa akses ini , plus ak mau rename file disini, gmn caranya"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"timestamp":1775393552921}}
{"type":"message","id":"1be19e23","parentId":"988b1aeb","timestamp":"2026-04-05T12:52:51.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke, 3 masalah di Vault mobile:\n\n1. **Harus landscape** — layout nggak responsive di portrait\n2. **Burger cuma ke landing** — butuh cara navigate tanpa sidebar\n3. **Nggak bisa rename file** — fitur belum ada\n\nLet me fix semua:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_O0O4IukFVQvGRyta614j5o","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/magi-v2/frontend/vault/index.html","limit":50}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":161,"cacheRead":270836,"cacheWrite":1337,"totalTokens":272337,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.004025,"cacheRead":0.13541799999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00835625,"total":0.14781424999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775393552953}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b481640","parentId":"1be19e23","timestamp":"2026-04-05T12:52:51.631Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_O0O4IukFVQvGRyta614j5o","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.json\"><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#060a14\"><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-capable\" content=\"yes\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\">\n<title>MAGI Vault</title>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/shared/core.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/shared/components.css\">\n<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest\"></script>\n<script src=\"/shared/marked.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/d3@7\"></script>\n<style>\n.app{display:flex;height:100vh;position:relative;z-index:1}\n\n/* ── Vault Sidebar ── */\n.vault-sidebar{width:240px;background:var(--bg-surface);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-right:1px solid var(--glass-border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;flex-shrink:0;transition:all .35s var(--ease-out);overflow:hidden}\n.vault-sidebar.collapsed{width:0;border:none}\n\n.sb-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:14px 14px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border)}\n.sb-logo{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.3px;flex:1;cursor:pointer;transition:opacity .2s;text-decoration:none}\n.sb-logo span{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--color-primary),var(--color-accent));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}\n.sb-logo:hover{opacity:.7}\n.sb-btn{width:28px;height:28px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;border-radius:6px;color:var(--text-tertiary);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}\n.sb-btn:hover{color:var(--text-secondary);background:var(--glass);border-color:var(--glass-border)}\n.sb-btn i{width:15px;height:15px}\n\n.sb-search{padding:8px 10px 6px}\n.sb-search-wrap{position:relative}\n.sb-search input{width:100%;padding:7px 10px 7px 30px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:8px;color:var(--text-primary);font-size:12px;font-family:var(--font-sans);outline:none;transition:all .2s}\n.sb-search input::placeholder{color:var(--text-tertiary)}\n.sb-search input:focus{border-color:var(--glass-border-hover);background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(129,140,248,.06)}\n.sb-search .icon{position:absolute;left:9px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);color:var(--text-tertiary);pointer-events:none}\n.sb-search .icon i{width:13px;height:13px}\n.search-results{position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 4px);left:0;right:0;max-height:260px;overflow-y:auto;background:var(--bg-elevated);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border:1px solid var(--glass-border-hover);border-radius:10px;z-index:50;display:none;box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}\n.search-results.active{display:block}\n.sr-item{padding:8px 12px;cursor:pointer;transition:background .15s;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border)}\n.sr-item:last-child{border:none}\n.sr-item:hover{background:var(--glass)}\n.sr-path{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)}\n.sr-snippet{font-size:10px;color:var(--text-tertiary);margin-top:2px;line-height:1.4}\n\n/* Tree */\n.file-tree{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:6px 4px}\n.tree-loading{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px;color:var(--text-tertiary);gap:8px;font-size:12px}\n.tree-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:4px 8px;margin:0 4px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);border-radius:6px;transition:all .15s;user-select:none;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden}\n.tree-item:hover{background:var(--glass);color:var(--text-primary)}\n.tree-item.active{background:var(--color-primary-dim);color:var(--text-primary);box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(129,140,248,.15)}\n.tree-item .indent{flex-shrink:0}\n.tree-item i{width:14px;height:14px;flex-shrink:0;opacity:.6}\n\n[502 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775393571615}}
