{"type":"message","id":"a4143bcf","parentId":"4d868abb","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:02:26.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNggak, Monitor page-nya bener kok. Itu data real dari backend — 12 agents, 1,825 total requests, $1.79 cost.\n\nYang mau kamu tanyain \"salah\" apanya? Apakah:\n\n1. **WhatsApp Handler = Uriel** — ini emang setting di MAGI v2, bukan OpenClaw. Kalau mau ganti ke Michael atau agent lain, bisa langsung dari dropdown itu.\n\n2. **\"0 active now\"** — karena yang jawab kamu sekarang itu Michael via OpenClaw (bukan MAGI v2 backend). MAGI agents track request yang masuk lewat MAGI chat, bukan WhatsApp.\n\n3. **\"8d ago\" last active** — semua agent last active 8 hari lalu karena nggak ada yang pakai MAGI chat langsung since then.\n\n4. **Sidebar icons** — kelihatan sidebar Apex udah jalan di desktop! 👀\n\nYang mana yang \"salah\" menurut kamu?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":267,"cacheRead":288201,"cacheWrite":1551,"totalTokens":290022,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.006675,"cacheRead":0.1441005,"cacheWrite":0.009693750000000001,"total":0.16048425}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775401333482}}
