{"type":"message","id":"d6564a18","parentId":"adc0b603","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:02:52.905Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nAh oke — itu cuma setting di *MAGI v2* frontend, bukan di OpenClaw gateway config. Yang handle WhatsApp kamu tetap **Michael via OpenClaw** — setting di MAGI Monitor itu buat routing internal MAGI aja.\n\nKalau kamu *beneran* mau Uriel yang handle WhatsApp (bukan Michael), itu harus diubah di OpenClaw gateway config, bukan di MAGI UI.\n\nMau gue ubah? Atau ini cuma testing aja di MAGI?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":139,"cacheRead":288201,"cacheWrite":832,"totalTokens":289175,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0034750000000000002,"cacheRead":0.1441005,"cacheWrite":0.005200000000000001,"total":0.1527905}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775401365445}}
