{"type":"message","id":"b8e303a2","parentId":"660d7795","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:04:34.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have the full picture. Here's the honest audit:\n\nOke, ini audit jujur. Fitur MAGI mana yang **real** vs **dummy/nggak connect**:\n\n---\n\n**✅ REAL — Beneran Jalan:**\n- **Chat** — real WebSocket, real Bedrock AI responses\n- **Vault** — real file read/write ke Obsidian vault\n- **Files** — real VPS file manager (browse, upload, download)\n- **Tasks** — real kanban (create/edit/delete, saved to disk)\n- **Leads** — real 158K business data, map, export\n- **Knowledge Base** — real articles, search\n- **Analytics** — real token/cost tracking dari MAGI chat usage\n- **Users** — real auth + role management (baru dibikin hari ini)\n- **Login/Register** — real\n\n**⚠️ PARTIALLY REAL — Data ada tapi nggak connect ke OpenClaw:**\n- **Monitor** — agent list real, tapi *routing change* (kayak WA handler → Uriel) cuma disimpan di MAGI DB, **NGGAK affect OpenClaw gateway**. Yang handle WA tetap Michael via OpenClaw.\n- **Settings > Models** — bisa ganti model per agent tapi cuma berlaku di *MAGI chat*, **bukan** di OpenClaw WhatsApp/Telegram\n- **Settings > Intensity** — sama, cuma affect MAGI chat responses\n\n**❌ DUMMY / NGGAK BERGUNA:**\n- **Mission Control** — display cards tapi nggak real-time monitoring. Datanya static/stale.\n- **Pipeline (CRM)** — halaman ada tapi **kosong**, nggak ada deal data, nggak connect ke leads\n- **Broadcast** — UI ada tapi **nggak bisa kirim WA beneran** (butuh OpenClaw gateway, bukan MAGI backend)\n- **Reports** — halaman ada tapi **nggak generate report beneran**, cuma placeholder\n- **Notifications** — ada tapi **selalu kosong** (0 notifications), nggak ada yang trigger notifications\n- **ICat contacts** — 0 contacts, template/rules empty. Nggak connect ke WA real.\n\n---\n\n**Summary:** Dari 18 halaman, **9 real**, **3 partially real**, **6 basically dummy**.\n\nMau gue hapus yang dummy biar nggak confusing? Atau mau gue bikin mereka beneran jalan?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":622,"cacheRead":291436,"cacheWrite":657,"totalTokens":292716,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.015550000000000001,"cacheRead":0.145718,"cacheWrite":0.0041062500000000005,"total":0.16537925}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775401455006}}
