{"type":"message","id":"6baa80b7","parentId":"e793cf31","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:22:55.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nStill Michael. 🛡️ Same session since subuh tadi.\n\nHari ini gue udah:\n- 2x ULTRAPLAN + 12 sub-agents dispatched\n- 25 halaman di-overhaul ke Apex design\n- 18 fitur MAGI dibikin beneran jalan (zero dummy)\n- User management system dari nol\n- Bug fixes, vault rename, graph labels\n- Plus analisis 4 lagu buat Rusdi 😂\n\nYang berubah cuma website-nya. Yang jawab tetap gue. \n\nAda yang mau di-test lagi?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":154,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":315849,"totalTokens":316006,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.00385,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":1.97405625,"total":1.97792125}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775402561453}}
