{"type":"message","id":"b8eb82a5","parentId":"f58b7276","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:24:25.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n100% jujur — **semua 18 fitur punya backend API yang real dan frontend yang connect ke API itu.** Nggak ada yang fake.\n\nTAPI — gue mau transparan:\n\n**Yang PASTI jalan (tested via API):**\n- ✅ Mission Control — live CPU/RAM/Disk/PM2 (tested `GET /api/system/status`)\n- ✅ Pipeline CRM — CRUD deals (tested create/update/delete)\n- ✅ Notifications — event triggers (tested, hooks di register + pipeline)\n- ✅ Reports — generate from real data (tested `POST /api/reports/generate`)\n- ✅ Chat, Vault, Files, Tasks, Leads, Knowledge, Users, Analytics, Monitor, Settings, ICat\n\n**Yang gue BELUM bisa 100% verify dari sisi gue:**\n- ⚠️ **Broadcast WA send** — backend code calls OpenClaw gateway di `http://127.0.0.1:18789/api/message`. Logika-nya benar, tapi gue belum test kirim pesan beneran lewat broadcast page. Mungkin perlu adjust endpoint-nya kalau gateway API format-nya beda.\n- ⚠️ **Frontend rendering** — 4 agents edit ~8 halaman secara parallel. Bisa ada CSS conflict atau JS error yang cuma keliatan di browser. Gue nggak bisa buka browser buat visual test.\n\n**Cara verify:** Buka tiap halaman, kalau ada yang error/blank/broken, screenshot → kirim ke gue → gue fix langsung.\n\nSo yeah — backend 100% real. Frontend 95% confident. Sisanya butuh kamu test di browser. Nggak ada yang dummy lagi. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":444,"cacheRead":315849,"cacheWrite":328,"totalTokens":316624,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0111,"cacheRead":0.1579245,"cacheWrite":0.00205,"total":0.1710895}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775402649265}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c4908ba","parentId":"b8eb82a5","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:26:18.498Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/8cdfebee-30bd-4aa9-9158-df6961bfe6b2.jpg (image/jpeg)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3EB0FC8F25E16E11347262\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nini fungsinya buat apa?"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"timestamp":1775402778444}}
{"type":"message","id":"4083f095","parentId":"2c4908ba","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:26:32.555Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nIni ngatur **agent voice** yang MAGI pakai waktu kirim pesan dari MAGI web.\n\nContoh: kalau kamu pakai fitur **Broadcast** atau **WhatsApp Send** dari MAGI dashboard, pesan yang dikirim akan pakai \"suara\" agent yang dipilih di sini.\n\n- *MAGI Send-As Agent (WhatsApp):* **Uriel** — jadi kalau MAGI kirim WA, responsenya pakai personality Uriel\n- *MAGI Send-As Agent (Telegram):* **Gabriel** — kalau kirim ke Telegram, pakai personality Gabriel\n\n**Yang BUKAN diatur di sini:** WhatsApp chat biasa kamu ke gue (Michael). Itu dihandle langsung oleh OpenClaw gateway — beda system, beda routing.\n\nBasically: OpenClaw = yang jawab chat kamu sehari-hari (Michael). MAGI = dashboard web yang punya kemampuan kirim pesan juga, dan dropdown ini pilih \"persona siapa yang dipake.\"\n\nKalau nggak pernah kirim pesan dari MAGI web, fitur ini nggak affect apa-apa. Mau gue sembunyiin atau biarin aja?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":307,"cacheRead":316177,"cacheWrite":957,"totalTokens":317444,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.007675,"cacheRead":0.1580885,"cacheWrite":0.0059812500000000005,"total":0.17175975}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775402778485}}
