{"type":"message","id":"17df5de3","parentId":"e3efd79b","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:32:16.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNggak bisa dari MAGI web — yang handle WhatsApp chat kamu itu **OpenClaw gateway**, bukan MAGI.\n\nKalau mau ganti dari Michael ke agent lain (misal Uriel atau Rafael), gue bisa ubah langsung dari sini. Tinggal bilang:\n\n- \"Ganti ke Uriel\" → yang jawab WA jadi Uriel\n- \"Ganti ke Rafael\" → yang jawab WA jadi Rafael\n\nAtau kalau kamu mau fitur switch agent dari MAGI web, gue bisa bikin. Tapi itu butuh MAGI web bisa call OpenClaw gateway API buat ganti config — slightly risky karena restart gateway tiap ganti.\n\nMau gue:\n1. **Ganti sekarang** via CLI? Ke agent mana?\n2. **Bikin fitur di MAGI web** buat switch? (lebih complex tapi convenient)\n3. **Biarin Michael** aja? 😄"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":253,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":317398,"totalTokens":317654,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.006325,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":1.9837375000000002,"total":1.9900775000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775403122085}}
