{"type":"message","id":"7d5007e4","parentId":"3b16871d","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:33:43.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Browser tool masih down. Tapi nggak usah install Droplet baru — yang paling efisien:\n\n**Kamu test, gue fix.** Caranya:\n\n1. Buka tiap halaman di HP/laptop\n2. Kalau **jalan & bagus** → skip\n3. Kalau **error/blank/broken** → screenshot kirim ke sini\n4. Gue fix dalam hitungan menit\n\nIni honestly lebih cepat daripada setup remote browser. Kamu jadi QA tester, gue jadi hotfix machine. \n\nChecklist buat test (urutan prioritas):\n1. ⬡ Dashboard (landing)\n2. 📡 Mission Control\n3. 🔄 Pipeline\n4. 📢 Broadcast\n5. 📋 Reports\n6. 🔔 Notifications\n7. 💬 Chat\n8. 🔐 Vault\n9. 📊 Monitor\n\nMau mulai dari mana?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":250,"cacheRead":317839,"cacheWrite":178,"totalTokens":318268,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.00625,"cacheRead":0.1589195,"cacheWrite":0.0011125,"total":0.166287}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775403213795}}
