{"type":"message","id":"144efa2c","parentId":"a1ea2dd2","timestamp":"2026-04-05T19:47:57.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGood question. Right now ULTRAPLAN runs in background — kamu cuma dapet result di akhir. Ada beberapa cara biar kamu bisa liat thinking process live:\n\n**Option 1: Stream to WhatsApp (Recommended)**\nGue modify ULTRAPLAN biar setiap phase kirim update ke kamu:\n- \"🧠 Reading 18 files...\"\n- \"🧠 Found 6 critical issues...\"\n- \"🧠 Designing architecture...\"\n- \"🧠 Planning 4-agent split...\"\n- \"✅ Plan complete\"\n\nBasically progress notifications while it thinks. Kamu nggak perlu buka apa-apa.\n\n**Option 2: Visual Explainer**\nAfter ULTRAPLAN selesai, gue auto-generate interactive HTML page yang breakdown the full thinking:\n- Problem analysis → decision tree → approach comparison → execution plan\n- Bisa buka di browser, scroll through, visual diagram\n\n**Option 3: MAGI Chat**\nRun ULTRAPLAN via MAGI web chat instead of WhatsApp. Di MAGI, response di-stream real-time — kamu liat token by token as Opus thinks.\n\n**Option 4: Reasoning Mode**\nGue enable \"thinking/reasoning\" pada sub-agent — ini expose internal chain-of-thought. Tapi ini nambah cost karena reasoning tokens lebih mahal.\n\n---\n\nWhich one kamu prefer? Atau combine — misal Option 1 (WA updates) + Option 2 (visual summary after)?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":368,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":373768,"totalTokens":374139,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0092,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":2.33605,"total":2.3452650000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775418459583}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca7e5331","parentId":"144efa2c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T19:50:38.940Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"AC5BADE6DE55ABDB49C2F2EF41514540\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nULTRAPLAN INI 3 AGENT Gimana kalau Opsi 2 dan 3 , jadi ad ULTRAPLAN atau nanti kita rename jadi DEEP THINK, Dan setelah sudah selesai debat keluarkan visual planner, also ak mau ad opsi agent dengan tambahan tombol 👼 untuk bisa menarik agent secara otomatis, WDYT"}],"timestamp":1775418638877}}
{"type":"message","id":"237d13cc","parentId":"ca7e5331","timestamp":"2026-04-05T19:50:58.708Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGue suka konsepnya. Let me break down:\n\n**1. DEEP THINK (rename dari ULTRAPLAN)**\n- 3 agents berdebat/brainstorm — bukan 1 Opus sendirian\n- Misal: Rafael (strategy) vs Uriel (technical) vs Samael (challenge assumptions)\n- Mereka argue, counter-argue, sampai converge ke plan terbaik\n- Setelah selesai → auto-generate **Visual Planner** (interactive HTML)\n\n**2. Visual Planner output**\n- Timeline view, decision tree, risk matrix\n- Bisa klik-klik expand details\n- Hosted di MAGI, bisa share link\n\n**3. 👼 Button — Auto-Pull Agent**\n- Di MAGI Chat/Roundtable, ada tombol 👼\n- Klik → AI analyze context percakapan → otomatis tarik agent yang paling relevan\n- Misal lagi bahas finance → 👼 auto-suggest Azrael\n- Lagi bahas security risk → 👼 auto-suggest Samael\n- User confirm atau dismiss\n\n**My take:**\n\nIni basically bikin MAGI jadi **self-orchestrating** — nggak perlu kamu manually pilih agent, system yang decide siapa yang harus ngomong based on context. \n\nYang perlu di-build:\n1. **Backend: `/api/deep-think`** — spawn 3 agents, collect responses, synthesize\n2. **Backend: `/api/suggest-agent`** — analyze message context, return recommended agent\n3. **Frontend: Deep Think UI** di MAGI (trigger, progress, visual output)\n4. **Frontend: 👼 button** di Chat + Roundtable\n5. **Visual Planner generator** (HTML template)\n\nMau gue DEEP THINK ini dulu (meta — deep think about deep think 😄), atau langsung build?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":471,"cacheRead":373768,"cacheWrite":623,"totalTokens":374865,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.011775,"cacheRead":0.186884,"cacheWrite":0.00389375,"total":0.20256775}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775418638925}}
