{"type":"message","id":"1653431e","parentId":"9edc5efe","timestamp":"2026-04-06T02:57:07.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ada SSH key! Tapi git belum configured. \n\n**Cara paling gampang:**\n1. Kamu kasih gue **GitHub Personal Access Token** (PAT) — bisa generate di GitHub Settings → Developer Settings → Personal Access Tokens → Fine-grained\n2. Gue set sebagai credential, terus bisa push/pull/clone\n\nAtau kalau mau pakai SSH key yang udah ada:\n1. Copy public key: gue kasih isinya\n2. Kamu tambah di GitHub Settings → SSH Keys\n\nMau yang mana? Atau ini buat apa dulu — push code MAGI ke repo?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":156,"cacheRead":381293,"cacheWrite":188,"totalTokens":381638,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0039000000000000003,"cacheRead":0.1906465,"cacheWrite":0.001175,"total":0.1957265}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775444217923}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a62f15a","parentId":"1653431e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:18:37.738Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"ACE025A48AAA6BE4BEB2F4030DD39A42\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285161502503\",\n  \"sender\": \"Kenny\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Kenny (+6285161502503)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285161502503\",\n  \"name\": \"Kenny\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285161502503\"\n}\n```\n\nhey, kamu bisa cariin produk tertentu di shopee ga? misalnya aku suruh cari baju lari lumayan murah as in 3 under 150k but also toko nya juga jual running belt bisa gak"}],"timestamp":1775445517660}}
{"type":"message","id":"7878689b","parentId":"0a62f15a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:18:58.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHei Kenny! 👋\n\nSayangnya gue **nggak bisa browse Shopee** langsung — Shopee butuh login + anti-bot protection yang nggak bisa gue bypass dari server.\n\n**Tapi** gue bisa bantu dengan cara lain:\n\n1. **Kasih rekomendasi keyword search** yang tepat buat kamu cari sendiri di Shopee:\n   - Cari: `\"baju lari pria\"` atau `\"running shirt dryfit\"` → sort harga terendah → filter harga max 50rb/pcs\n   - Terus cek toko yang sama, liat apakah mereka jual `\"running belt\"` juga\n\n2. **Tips cari toko yang jual keduanya:**\n   - Cari `\"running belt\"` dulu\n   - Filter: rating 4.5+, pengiriman dari Jawa (biasa lebih murah)\n   - Masuk toko yang jual running belt → browse produk toko → cari baju lari mereka\n   - Toko sport kayak **Decathlon Official**, **JYFD Sport**, **Rockbros Official** biasa jual keduanya\n\n3. **Budget 3 baju under 150K:**\n   - Range 30-50K/pcs itu bisa dapet dryfit basic yang decent\n   - Brand lokal: Mills, Specs, Ortuseight — sering promo\n   - Running belt biasa 25-60K yang basic\n\nMau gue cariin via web search buat rekomendasiin toko/produk specific? Nggak bisa buka Shopee tapi bisa cari review & rekomendasi dari forum/artikel."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":427,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":381832,"totalTokens":382262,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.010675,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":2.38645,"total":2.39714}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775445517719}}
