{"type":"message","id":"138e7993","parentId":"38684a90","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:38:19.347Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_XV6n49wKDMVUVV4w5vnIAJ","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"197:/* 👼 Auto-Agent Button */\n198:.angel-btn{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:var(--radius-md);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.15);background:rgba(245,158,11,.04);color:#f59e0b;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out)}\n199:.angel-btn:hover{background:rgba(245,158,11,.12);border-color:rgba(245,158,11,.3);box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(245,158,11,.2);transform:translateY(-1px)}\n308:        <button class=\"angel-btn\" id=\"angelBtn\" onclick=\"window._suggestAgent()\" title=\"Auto-select best agent\">👼</button>\n769:// ── Auto-Agent (👼) ──\n770:async function suggestAgent(){\n774:  const btn=$('angelBtn');if(btn){btn.style.opacity='.5';btn.style.pointerEvents='none'}\n779:      toast('👼 Suggested: '+(data.agentName||data.agentId),'success');\n786:window._suggestAgent=suggestAgent;"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":41,"aggregated":"197:/* 👼 Auto-Agent Button */\n198:.angel-btn{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:var(--radius-md);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.15);background:rgba(245,158,11,.04);color:#f59e0b;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out)}\n199:.angel-btn:hover{background:rgba(245,158,11,.12);border-color:rgba(245,158,11,.3);box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(245,158,11,.2);transform:translateY(-1px)}\n308:        <button class=\"angel-btn\" id=\"angelBtn\" onclick=\"window._suggestAgent()\" title=\"Auto-select best agent\">👼</button>\n769:// ── Auto-Agent (👼) ──\n770:async function suggestAgent(){\n774:  const btn=$('angelBtn');if(btn){btn.style.opacity='.5';btn.style.pointerEvents='none'}\n779:      toast('👼 Suggested: '+(data.agentName||data.agentId),'success');\n786:window._suggestAgent=suggestAgent;","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775446699318}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f53987c","parentId":"138e7993","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:38:29.848Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ada! Line 308 — button 👼 di sebelah input chat. Cek di:\n\n**MAGI → Chat** → lihat di bawah, sebelah tombol Send, ada button kecil **👼** (warna gold/amber).\n\n**Cara pakai:**\n1. Ketik message dulu di input (misal \"berapa budget marketing bulan ini?\")\n2. Klik 👼\n3. AI auto-suggest agent terbaik (misal Azrael buat budget)\n4. Auto-switch ke Private mode dengan agent itu\n\nKalau masih nggak keliatan, mungkin perlu hard refresh (Ctrl+Shift+R). Atau screenshot chat page-nya — gue check posisinya."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":185,"cacheRead":390402,"cacheWrite":473,"totalTokens":391061,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.004625000000000001,"cacheRead":0.19520099999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00295625,"total":0.20278724999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775446699363}}
