{"type":"message","id":"3ed20ea3","parentId":"184758c6","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:50:25.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**Jina AI** (jina.ai) — company yang bikin tools buat AI/search. Yang gue pakai dari mereka:\n\n**r.jina.ai** — \"Reader\" service. Gue prepend `https://r.jina.ai/` di depan URL apapun → dia return clean markdown text dari halaman itu. Bypass JavaScript rendering, anti-bot, dll.\n\nContoh:\n- `https://r.jina.ai/https://x.com/tom_doerr` → dapet text content Twitter tanpa perlu login\n\nGue pakai ini karena banyak website (Twitter, Genius, Fandom, dll) block direct fetch dari server. Jina Reader acts as middleman yang render page-nya dulu baru kasih text-nya ke gue.\n\n**Gratis** buat basic use, nggak perlu API key. Kadang di-throttle kalau terlalu banyak request (kayak tadi — makanya beberapa Tom Dörr posts nggak ke-load).\n\nBasically gue pakai mereka sebagai \"mata\" buat baca web. Bukan orang, bukan company yang penting — cuma tool. 🔧"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":296,"cacheRead":402571,"cacheWrite":863,"totalTokens":403733,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0074,"cacheRead":0.20128549999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00539375,"total":0.21409424999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775447410803}}
