{"type":"message","id":"d11d96ad","parentId":"a2b96b86","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:51:43.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBisa — tapi gue butuh **Personal Access Token** (PAT) dari kamu. Nggak bisa login pakai username/password karena GitHub enforce 2FA.\n\n**Cara generate PAT (2 menit):**\n\n1. Buka: https://github.com/settings/tokens?type=beta\n2. Klik **\"Generate new token\"**\n3. Name: `michael-vps`\n4. Expiration: 90 days\n5. Repository access: **All repositories**\n6. Permissions: **Contents** (read & write), **Metadata** (read)\n7. Generate → copy token\n\nKirim token-nya ke gue, gue set di VPS. Setelah itu gue bisa:\n- Create repos\n- Push all MAGI code, D&D app, skills, workspace\n- Commit & version control everything\n- Auto-backup via cron\n\n**Apa aja yang mau gue push ke GitHub:**\n- `magi-v2/` — full MAGI dashboard (frontend + backend)\n- `council-room/` — legacy council + IT support\n- `dnd-app/` — Paul Simulator\n- `skills/` — semua custom skills yang kita build\n- OpenClaw workspace configs\n\nMau sekalian atau pilih-pilih?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":321,"cacheRead":403434,"cacheWrite":497,"totalTokens":404255,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.008025000000000001,"cacheRead":0.20171699999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00310625,"total":0.21286324999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775447490704}}
